Title: Jones and His New Neighbors
Actors: John R. Cumpson, Florence Lawrence, Anita Hendrie
Plot: The Joneses have moved and taken an apartment in one of a row of houses which are identically alike. The most natural thing happens: Jones gets into the wrong house, and, of course, his intrusion is vigorously resented, and it looked for a time he would suffer bodily injury, but, as usual, the menacing clouds dissipate and peace again reigns in the Jones domicile. Eddy may get some hard bumps, but they never scar.
